<div class="container" style="padding-top: 5%;">
	<div class="clearfix">
	<form class="form col col-6" action="/projects" method="post">
		All fields are required.<br>
		<label>Name:</label>
		<input class="block half-width field-light" type="text" name="project[name]"/>
		<label>Description:</label>
		<textarea class="block half-width field-light" name="project[description]"></textarea>
		<label>Website:</label>
		<input class="block half-width field-light" type="text" name="project[production_url]"/>
		<label>Github:</label>
		<input class="block half-width field-light" type="text" name="project[source_url]"/>
		<label>Location:</label>
		<select class="block half-width field-light" name="project[location">
			<option></option>
			<option>San Francisco</option>
			<option>Chicago</option>
			<option>New York</option>
		</select>
		<label>Image Url</label>
		<input class="block half-width field-light" type="text" name="project[image_url]"/>
		<label>What technologies did your team use?</label>
		<input class="block half-width field-light" type="text" name="project[answer1]"/>
		<label>What was your biggest technical challenge?</label>
		<input class="block half-width field-light" type="text" name="project[answer2]"/>
		<label>If you could do it over again, what would you change?</label>
		<input class="block half-width field-light" type="text" name="project[answer3]"/>
		<label>What advice do you have for people about to begin their final projects? </label>
		<input class="block half-width field-light" type="text" name="project[answer4]"/>
		<button type="submit" class="button-blue">Submit</button>
	</form>
	</div>
</div>